            team_bio_1_p1: "CEO of Axia Group, a business consulting and management firm operating in Brazil and abroad, with a DNA of future vision, focus on results, and innovative solutions that guarantee the highest levels of value.",
            team_bio_1_p2: "Possesses solid experience and leadership in TAP/PID (project charter / Project Initiation Document) projects \"started from scratch\", with specialization in operation management across industry, trade, and agribusiness, focusing on innovation, technology, and sustainability.",
