            team_bio_2_p1: "Administrator, advertiser and entrepreneur with a strong presence in Brazil and Portugal. Born in Espírito Santo, resides between Serra/ES and Lisbon/PT, accumulating more than 25 years of experience in the digital marketing, business management and strategic communication sectors.",
